      </li>

        <li><strong>Non-Disclosure:</strong> You will not disclose by word of mouth or otherwise, particulars or details of 
business plans /trade I secret /finance [know how and 
or any confidential information of business coming to your knowledge by virtue of your being in the 
employment of amazon IT solutions.</li>
        <li><strong>Acceptance:</strong> If you accept the above terms and conditions of the service, please signify your 
acceptance by signing up the photo copy of this Appointment letter thereof otherwise this letter of 
appointment will be deemed to have been withdrawn and cancelled.</li>
</ol>

  <div class="signature">
  <!-- <p style="margin-bottom: 4px;"><strong>Yours Sincerely,</strong></p> -->
  <p class="for" style="margin-bottom: 2px;">For <%= companyName %></p>
  <% if (signaturePath) { %>
    <div style="margin: -6px 0 3px 12px; display: inline-block;">
      <img src="<%= signaturePath %>" alt="Authorized Signature" style="width:80px; height:auto; opacity:0.95;" />
    </div>
  <% } %>
  <p class="signer">Chakravarthy Devarkonda</p>
  <p style="margin-top: -8px;">Manager – Human Resources.</p>
</div>
    </div>
    </div>

  <!-- ===== PAGE 4: ANNEXURE ===== -->
  <!-- PAGE 4: Annexure -->
<div class="page">
  <% if (letterheadPath) { %><img src="<%= letterheadPath %>" class="letterhead" /><% } %>

  <div class="content">
    <p style="text-align:justify; margin-top:15px;">
  This is to certify that I, 
  <strong style="text-decoration: underline;"><%= appointment.employeeName || "" %></strong>, 
  have read and understood all the above-mentioned terms 
  and conditions and I hereby accept without any duress or coercion, and agree to the offer.
</p>


    <p style="margin-top:30px; text-align:left;">
      Date: _________________ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Place: _________________ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Signature: ________________
    </p><br/>

    <!-- ===== Annexure Title ===== -->
    <h3 class="annexure-title">Annexure-I</p>
    <!-- <p style="text-align:center; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.3px; margin-bottom:10px;">
      SALARY COMPUTATION
    </p> -->

    <!-- ===== Salary Table ===== -->
    <table>
        <colgroup>
          <col style="width: 65%;" />
          <col style="width: 17.5%;" />
          <col style="width: 17.5%;" />
        </colgroup>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th colspan="3" style="text-align: center;">SALARY COMPUTATION</th>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>Components</th>
            <th>Per annum</th>
            <th>Per Month</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <% (appointment.salaryComponents || []).forEach(function(row){ %>
            <tr>
              <td><%= row.label %></td>
              <td><%= Number(row.perAnnum || 0).toLocaleString('en-IN') %></td>
              <td><%= Number(row.perMonth || 0).toLocaleString('en-IN') %></td>
            </tr>
          <% }); %>
        </tbody>
      </table>
 <br/><br/>
    <!-- ===== Notes Below Table ===== -->
    <div class="note">
      
      <h4 style="font-size: 13px; font-family: calibri, serif !important; margin: 6px 0 2px 0; text-align: left;">Procedure for standard reimbursement:</h4>
     
      <p style="font-size: 13px; margin: 0 0 5px 0;">
        The LTA can be claimed against production of bills at the end of the financial year subject to provision of Income TaxAct. Any unclaimed amount will be paid to you at the end of the financial year after deducting the necessary taxes.
      </p><br/></br>
      <p style="text-align:center; font-size:13px;">
      <strong>Note:</strong> This is a computer-generated document. No Signature is required*.
    </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
